@page
@model SignsModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Signs";
}

<main>
    <div>
        <h2>Zodiac Signs</h2>

        <h4>Aries (March 21 - April 19)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Ram</h6>
        <p>Energetic and passionate, Aries individuals are known for their enthusiasm, courage, and independent spirit. They are natural leaders who are often the first to take charge and initiate new projects.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Taurus (April 20 - May 20)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Bull</h6>
        <p>Reliable and grounded, Taurus individuals are known for their determination, practicality, and love of comfort. They are often patient and persistent, and they have a strong appreciation for the finer things in life.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Gemini (May 21 - June 20)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Twins</h6>
        <p>Curious and adaptable, Gemini individuals are known for their versatility, intelligence, and communication skills. They are often social and enjoy engaging in lively conversations and debates.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Cancer (June 21 - July 22)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Crab</h6>
        <p>Nurturing and emotional, Cancer individuals are known for their sensitivity, empathy, and loyalty. They are often protective of their loved ones and enjoy creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Leo (July 23 - August 22)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Lion</h6>
        <p>Confident and charismatic, Leo individuals are known for their creativity, generosity, and leadership qualities. They often enjoy being the center of attention and thrive in the spotlight.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Virgo (August 23 - September 22)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Virgin</h6>
        <p>Practical and analytical, Virgo individuals are known for their attention to detail, intelligence, and helpful nature. They are often perfectionists who strive for excellence in all that they do.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Libra (September 23 - October 22)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Scales</h6>
        <p>Diplomatic and harmonious, Libra individuals are known for their fairness, charm, and social grace. They often seek balance and harmony in their relationships and surroundings.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Scorpio (October 23 - November 21)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Scorpion</h6>
        <p>Intense and passionate, Scorpio individuals are known for their determination, resourcefulness, and magnetic personality. They are often deeply intuitive and have a strong sense of mystery.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Sagittarius (November 22 - December 21)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Archer</h6>
        <p>Optimistic and adventurous, Sagittarius individuals are known for their enthusiasm, independence, and philosophical outlook. They often have a thirst for knowledge and a desire to explore new horizons.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Capricorn (December 22 - January 19)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Sea-Goat</h6>
        <p>Ambitious and disciplined, Capricorn individuals are known for their responsibility, perseverance, and leadership qualities. They are often goal-oriented and strive for success in their careers and personal lives.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Aquarius (January 20 - February 18)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Water-Bearer</h6>
        <p>Independent and unconventional, Aquarius individuals are known for their originality, intelligence, and humanitarian spirit. They often embrace individuality and challenge traditional norms.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4>Pisces (February 19 - March 20)</h4>
        <h6>Symbol: The Fish</h6>
        <p>Compassionate and intuitive, Pisces individuals are known for their empathy, creativity, and spiritual nature. They often have a strong connection to their emotions and a deep understanding of the human condition.</p>
    </div>
</main>